Usage: FORMAT DCC_CHAT_ACTION <format description>
  Controls how actions transmitted through DCC CHAT appear

  Valid format characters:
       F          Nick of person doing action
       M          The action message

See Also:  
  ME
  DESCRIBE
  DCC CHAT
